              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Numbers 19:1</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And the LORD spake unto Moses and unto Aaron, saying,</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And Jehovah speaketh unto Moses, and unto Aaron, saying,</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">And Jehovah<S>3068</S> spake<S>1696</S> unto Moses<S>4872</S> and unto Aaron<S>175</S>, saying<S>559</S>,</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Yahweh spoke to Moses and to Aaron, saying,</span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
              <div style="font-family:var(--font-heading);color:var(--gold);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:0.5rem;font-weight:600;">Numbers 19:2</div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--leather-dark);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">KJV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">This is the ordinance of the law which the LORD hath commanded, saying, Speak unto the children of Israel, that they bring thee a red heifer without spot, wherein is no blemish, and upon which never came yoke:</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">'This [is] a statute of the law which Jehovah hath commanded, saying, Speak unto the sons of Israel, and they bring unto thee a red cow, a perfect one, in which there is no blemish, on which no yoke hath gone up;</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">This is the statute<S>2708</S> of the law<S>8451</S> which Jehovah<S>3068</S> hath commanded<S>6680</S>, saying<S>559</S>, Speak<S>1696</S> unto the children<S>1121</S> of Israel<S>3478</S>, that they bring<S>3947</S> thee a red<S>122</S> heifer<S>6510</S> without spot<S>8549</S>, wherein is no blemish<S>3971</S>, and upon which never<S>3808</S> came<S>5927</S> yoke<S>5923</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">“This is the statute of the law which Yahweh has commanded. Tell the children of Israel to bring you a red heifer without spot, in which is no defect, and which was never yoked.</span></div>
            </div>
            <div style="margin-bottom:1.5rem;padding-bottom:1.5rem;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(197,150,12,0.15);">
