              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">and the priest hath taken cedar wood, and hyssop, and scarlet, and hath cast unto the midst of the burning of the cow;</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">and the priest<S>3548</S> shall take<S>3947</S> cedar<S>730</S> - wood<S>6086</S>, and hyssop<S>231</S>, and scarlet<S>8438</S>, and cast<S>7993</S> it into the midst<S>8432</S> of the burning<S>8316</S> of the heifer<S>6510</S>.</span></div>
              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">The priest shall take cedar wood, hyssop, and scarlet, and cast it into the middle of the burning of the heifer.</span></div>
